This is the by-chapter-number version of theCompact Disc Interactive Full Functional Specification(Green Book).  Figures is the collected list of figuresfor all chapters.  Preface is the preface to the Green Book.Contents is the collected Table of Contents for all chapters.Chap1-8 are Chapters I through VIII of the Green Book.App1-8 are Appendices I through VIII of the Green Book.The by-name versions of these files are present in ../by_name.